race.comment: HAVEN'S JOY (1) is better than last start when seventh (20.67) in a Grade 5 at this track over 352m. Solid formlines coming through her last run. Better than last start and worth following up. AQUA LILIUM (2) turned in a plain performance last time when fifth at this track over 390m behind Hope's Zone (22.17) in a OPEN. Was in the money the start prior. One of the main contenders. ABODE'S TRILOGY (5) should be thereabouts after filling a top-three spot most recently.
